{"tid":1375572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"接送攻略！唔該車手們入嚟睇下！！！","createTime":"2019-07-28T05:52:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T02:35:43.000Z","uid":261925,"like":104,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"b18e570853d2b88bce0fc633a5294421fbb4c5b7","tid":1375572,"uid":261925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:52:34.000Z","msg":"今次又借朋友acc用，請各位手下留情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港城市規劃係以公共交通，尤其鐵路為中心。單從資源角度來看，即使香港汽車數量連年創新高，相對抗爭人數而言，仍相當稀少。而且汽車功能多樣化，集載客、載貨、偵察、臨時急救車於一身，24/7可用，難有替代品，屬重要的戰略資源，值得嚴格保護。<strong>應該要盡量保障返司機同汽車本身，缺一不可的，人或車黃左，下次就無得再用，唔好咁易比人周到。</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>絕對唔建議長打死火燈</strong><br />\n事關接送group其實係公海，屌你唔係以為無鬼滲透呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一定有人起相關地點捕住mark車牌。今日就見過肌肉大隻佬、又有疑似madam、鄉黑、自發藍絲，拎住電話，起各大接送地點四處遊盪左勁耐。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>乘客上車前必須變裝</strong><br />\n係必須！！！由頭到腳！！！越融入該地區越好。以地區劃分，港島戰線多是返工look及落bar look，沙田是偽中產扮靚周末約會look，屯天元是街坊look。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">千祈唔好口罩黑衫4條友一齊衝上車</span></strong><br />\n司機巴打尋晚話：<br />\n「你班人即刻敲下自己個柒腦，諗下自己點撚解要坐車。你唔想俾人見到丫嘛係咪？屌你，你真係十萬火急死人冧樓，元朗721咁，乘客司機你情我願，冇問題。而家講緊平常撤退，屌你，做乜撚嘢見到架車，急到瀨咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「唔怕嘅我地四個上車好快架啫」個死款，仆你個街，忽然心存僥倖？屌你有啲連把長遮都自己碌九咁拎撚住唔放就咁上車，係咪真係咁on撚鳩？？今日啲車cam片我睇左幾次，見到都眼冤。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你班人搭順風車就識，知唔知而家幾多車黃左？我係藍絲嘅話，你地半個元朗連埋班司機死撚左十九萬世啦柒頭！！！<br />\n如俾狗即場認到車牌，前面路障查你五個又得，暗中起司機底慢慢查又得，你點撚樣防呀請問！！」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>上車前搵個冇cctv嘅地方變身</strong><br />\n巴打笠恤衫，絲打換半截裙，背囊等物資用大tote bag入住。司機也可以事先準備，請副駕拿去給小朋友換衫。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>接送地點不要點對點</strong><br />\n下車勿令地址曝光。上車也不要離戰場太近，約步行15-30分鐘位置為佳。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>司機及副駕位，要令人較沒有戒心。</strong><br />\n同絲打拍拖又得，家庭式帶銀髮、小朋友又得。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你司機自己一個出，係會接多一位，但就冇咩偽裝，自己衡量。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>副駕很重要</strong><br />\n可以即時報Roadblock位置上客位置等等，唔好on99送頭。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>過Roadblock必須要有故事背景</strong><br />\n時地人好好考慮合理性。自由發揮<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">727mvp良好示範</span></strong><br />\n見有離場男士穿 casual恤衫。中型背包前孭，或用醜醜的奶粉宣傳環保袋。<br />\n<br />\n----------<br />\n今朝司機巴打心情好返啲，話：<br />\n<br />\n各位車主，要諗下點樣用自己嘅資源，偽裝一下自己架車。你一個熱血年輕人，揸架錢七，停外圈打死火燈，個副駕仲要黑衫口罩，唔留意你留意邊個？唔單止人要融入，係連架車都要偽裝。你車型，係咩人揸多？配合返。<strong>留意下藍絲廢老，點樣裝飾自己架車。</strong>飾物多就易認，冇飾物就冇偽裝（多數係），自己攞返個平行點。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">祝各位巴打絲打接放學順順利利！</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac07e9f59361270f7b8fc6ad308e53bcc78a6bfb","tid":1375572,"uid":11436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:55:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9c54e86020085042a12dcc7735e9c73d08226108","tid":1375572,"uid":261925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:10:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b084eebd4443e787750392b303e86971781b5ca","tid":1375572,"uid":261925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:11:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b79d8807b60a8478360cffe3cf4d24c607d6fd4b","tid":1375572,"uid":261925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:12:36.000Z","msg":"推到有需要嘅手足見到"},{"pid":"75fe762c8a73eab9a8d3562d0bb5a0b9f419aa59","tid":1375572,"uid":272805,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:12:41.000Z","msg":"要錄音問佢係唔係警察<br />\n答唔係先好諗上唔上車"},{"pid":"ad7b200765546b24b0585e1742d6d1345332de7f","tid":1375572,"uid":35125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:12:49.000Z","msg":"push 大家小心假義載"},{"pid":"e5e90996aec9354ff09dcda4ecc85dcc5a2183df","tid":1375572,"uid":44751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:13:19.000Z","msg":"點防到假車"},{"pid":"2b1814129e81dc1d77b1db16533891f287d6dac2","tid":1375572,"uid":151304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:13:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"371fbd7aae921b28d588cbfb576eda09db1f07ed","tid":1375572,"uid":73914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:13:43.000Z","msg":"好重要 推"},{"pid":"9136847ba53bc3026fcdb8077da91759c32fd291","tid":1375572,"uid":75514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:14:42.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"06614c986217dd03a38daab4ab013b6cde7fbbd0","tid":1375572,"uid":199244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:14:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6c075634cb6d3343e83dcc2998c33b6d1ce216ff","tid":1375572,"uid":235348,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:16:19.000Z","msg":"其實好似尋晚咁，附近已經有兩個西鐵站，車手出去仲有無意義？有咩可以做？<br />\n利申：有車，尋晚想出，但見交通無咩問題，大家都走到，又唔太熟路廢事搞喎左件事，最後無出。"},{"pid":"38f7ba3442df480a115a7a1ddaeaeb0525bc395f","tid":1375572,"uid":35556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:16:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2959d8e3aa14431e7144a3331b53071d06bf0b0e","tid":1375572,"uid":261925,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e5e90996aec9354ff09dcda4ecc85dcc5a2183df","tid":1375572,"uid":44751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:13:19.000Z","msg":"點防到假車"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:17:04.000Z","msg":"發夢見到通常係大隻仔，白色KIA，車身無貼紙無改裝。另外見到有巴打話拍住片問佢係咪警察，因為佢地唔可以答唔係。"},{"pid":"2dac512578ddc8736324029da3671ea42bd1dc7f","tid":1375572,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:17:50.000Z","msg":"保障大家  <br />\n大家都開定位 <br />\n5分鐘要聯絡友人一次  <br />\n冇聯絡即係出左事  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小心鄉黑扮司機乘客"},{"pid":"aaf8095a60cb2b62104a64140e19822783be3b8b","tid":1375572,"uid":49580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:20:43.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"96ded81f2433ca468e09b19ea5c50e05f2110eaa","tid":1375572,"uid":189484,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:28:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fy38vD6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffy38vD6.png&h=abc8bdb6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/30i8vD7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F30i8vD7.png&h=289e31f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z50uZxs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz50uZxs.png&h=56e3a2ae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hwdsMct.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhwdsMct.png&h=3a049a9b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/arsk6ct.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Farsk6ct.png&h=eb61895a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到呢幾款車，自己要小心"},{"pid":"2f1b3ff65c2e34a854fe7323806b52b715b2c38c","tid":1375572,"uid":189484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:30:50.000Z","msg":"仲有Toyota Prius 同埋萬事得 Biante"},{"pid":"01c3f28f35fcf983423715ae236d8208da35208c","tid":1375572,"uid":1667,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"96ded81f2433ca468e09b19ea5c50e05f2110eaa","tid":1375572,"uid":189484,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T06:28:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fy38vD6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffy38vD6.png&h=abc8bdb6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/30i8